Kuchars Dokumentationen seiner unorthodoxen Suche nach Tornados im Mittleren Westen der USA.Neben einer Analyse der Videos unter besonderer Berücksichtigung von Kuchars am Hollywoodkino geschulter Naturdarstellung und seiner campen Repräsentation erhabener Wetterphänomene enthält der Band ein extensives Interview mit dem Künstler - eines der letzten, das er vor seinem Tod gegeben hat.  aGeorge Kuchar (1942-2011) was one of the most important directors of American underground film. Weather Diaries is a key work from his extensive oeuvre. Ulrich Ziemons' study is the first comprehensive German language portrayal of Kuchar's documentation of his unorthodox tornado hunting in the midwestern United States.In addition to an analysis of the videos with special consideration forKuchar's Hollywood-trained cinematic depiction of nature and his representation of sublime weather phenomena, the volume contains an extensive interview with the artist, one of the last which he gave before his death.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mrz 2022) 0aExperimental filmsxProduction and directionxHistory and criticism. 0aExperimental filmszUnited StatesxHistory and criticism. 0aMotion picture producers and directorszUnited StatesvBiography. 0aMotion picture producers and directorszUnited StatesvInterviews. 4aCamp. 4aDiary. 4aGeorge Kuchar. 4aMedienwissenschaft. 4aUnderground. 4aWetter. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Media Studies.2bisacsh  aMedia Studies.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2014z9783110370416oZDB-23-DSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyter